projects.name: Workout Analysis App
bullets: Led the development of WorkoutPal, a workout analysis app that uses YoloV8 pose estimation and computer vision to give users feedback on their workout, including repetition analysis, caloric estimation and form feedback.
Designed and developed an end to end ML pipeline that serves model inference to a SwiftUI iOS application using AWS to host API.

projects.name: Pursuit Labs - Task Management AI
bullets: As part of a startup accelerator, led the initial development and ideation of an AI-powered task management platform for mid-to-large scale companies.
Achieved 2nd place and secured $5,000 funding at the 2021 Canadian Undergraduate Conference on AI (CUCAI), showcasing early-stage success and product innovation.
